extends Object
implements SinglebandImageProcessor<T,S>
    Extract a polygon from an image. The output image will just contain the polygon. The polygon is rasterised using a ScanRasteriser.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
